                       GADTs
                       ConstraintKinds
                       MultiParamTypeClasses
                       TypeSynonymInstances
                       FlexibleInstances
                       FlexibleContexts
                       DeriveFunctor
                       DeriveFoldable
                       DeriveTraversable
